552
00:45:07,052 --> 00:45:08,815
Jo Pilyeon.

553
00:45:10,748 --> 00:45:11,786
Cái gì?

554
00:45:12,043 --> 00:45:13,625
Jo Pilyeon?

555
00:45:14,338 --> 00:45:16,817
Hắn chắc chắn là một sĩ quan cấp cao,

556
00:45:16,987 --> 00:45:18,855
